  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Face your worst school nightmares with nothing but paper airplanes! </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into gameplay set in an exaggerated school setting. Along the way, you’ll encounter a variety of enemies, each with their own strengths and weaknesses. Besides defeating them, you’ll also need to focus on collecting the pocket money they drop, which you can spend at the school store. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217440/extras/ba3bbaaad1b3533f06b42987c36e44cb.poster.avif?t=1738011842\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217440/extras/ba3bbaaad1b3533f06b42987c36e44cb.webm?t=1738011842\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217440/extras/ba3bbaaad1b3533f06b42987c36e44cb.mp4?t=1738011842\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Between levels, you can buy new items, choose your school persona, and upgrade your paper airplanes — every decision could be crucial to your success in later stages.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217440/extras/5f97fd3725b705db32dec4da33c17e64.avif?t=1738011842\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217440/extras_big/5f97fd3725b705db32dec4da33c17e64.avif?t=1738011842 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Besides the standard enemies, you’ll face bosses that embody your most dreaded school fears!</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >During the boss fights, each one enters a unique rage mode, adding an extra challenge to the battle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217440/extras/9d87793653b512d25580e2ae6f4385f5.poster.avif?t=1738011842\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217440/extras/9d87793653b512d25580e2ae6f4385f5.webm?t=1738011842\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217440/extras/9d87793653b512d25580e2ae6f4385f5.mp4?t=1738011842\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
